org.locationtech.geowave.core.ingest.avro

Interface GeoWaveAvroPluginBase<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GeoWaveAvroSchemaProvider
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GeoWaveAvroFormatPlugin<I,O>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLocalIngestWithMapper, AbstractSimpleFeatureIngestPlugin, AbstractStageWholeFileToAvro, GDELTIngestPlugin, GeoLifeIngestPlugin, GeoWaveAvroIngestPlugin, GpxIngestPlugin, Stanag4676IngestPlugin, TdriveIngestPlugin, TwitterIngestPlugin

    public interface GeoWaveAvroPluginBase<T>
extends GeoWaveAvroSchemaProvider
    All plugins based off of staged intermediate data (either reading or writing) must implement this interface. For handling intermediate data, the GeoWave ingestion framework has standardized on Avro for java object serialization and an Avro schema must be provided for handling any intermediate data.
